<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-08-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-08-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="141" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d141">
                            <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to
                                    General <persName type="to">Chaffee</persName>.</hi></head>
                            <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Received by General Chaffee,
                                    Toitsun, August 8, 1900.]</seg></opener>
                            <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Pekin</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-04"><hi rend="italic">August 4,
                                        1900</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                            <p>Situation more critical, but we will hold on until your arrival; hope
                                it will be soon. Send such information as you can.</p>
                            <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Conger.</hi></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>